{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Ben Roche: So I'm Ben, by the way."},{"time":2000,"text":"Homaro Cantu: And I'm Homaro."},{"time":4000,"text":"BR: And we're chefs. So when Moto"},{"time":6000,"text":"opened in 2004, people didn't really know"},{"time":8000,"text":"what to expect. A lot of people thought"},{"time":10000,"text":"that it was a Japanese restaurant, and"},{"time":12000,"text":"maybe it was the name, maybe it was"},{"time":14000,"text":"the logo, which was like a Japanese"},{"time":16000,"text":"character, but anyway, we had all these"},{"time":18000,"text":"requests for Japanese food, which is"},{"time":20000,"text":"really not what we did. And after about"},{"time":22000,"text":"the ten thousandth request for a maki roll,"},{"time":24000,"text":"we decided to give the people"},{"time":26000,"text":"what they wanted. So this picture is"},{"time":28000,"text":"an example of printed food, and this was"},{"time":30000,"text":"the first foray into what we like to call"},{"time":32000,"text":"flavor transformation. So this is all"},{"time":34000,"text":"the ingredients, all the flavor of, you know,"},{"time":36000,"text":"a standard maki roll, printed onto"},{"time":38000,"text":"a little piece of paper."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40000,"text":"HC: So our diners started to get bored"},{"time":42000,"text":"with this idea, and we decided to give them"},{"time":44000,"text":"the same course twice, so here we actually"},{"time":47000,"text":"took an element from the maki roll and"},{"time":49000,"text":"and took a picture of a dish and then"},{"time":51000,"text":"basically served that picture with the dish."},{"time":54000,"text":"So this dish in particular is basically"},{"time":56000,"text":"champagne with seafood."},{"time":58000,"text":"The champagne grapes that you see are"},{"time":60000,"text":"actually carbonated grapes. A little bit of"},{"time":62000,"text":"seafood and some cr√®me fraiche and the"},{"time":64000,"text":"picture actually tastes exactly like the dish. (Laughter)"},{"time":67000,"text":"BR: But it's not all just edible pictures."},{"time":69000,"text":"We decided to do something"},{"time":71000,"text":"a little bit different and transform flavors"},{"time":73000,"text":"that were very familiar -- so in this case,"},{"time":76000,"text":"we have carrot cake."},{"time":78000,"text":"So we take a carrot cake, put it"},{"time":80000,"text":"in a blender, and we have kind of like"},{"time":82000,"text":"a carrot cake juice, and then that went into"},{"time":84000,"text":"a balloon frozen in liquid nitrogen to create"},{"time":86000,"text":"this hollow shell of carrot cake"},{"time":89000,"text":"ice cream, I guess, and it comes off"},{"time":91000,"text":"looking like, you know,"},{"time":93000,"text":"Jupiter's floating around your plate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95000,"text":"So yeah, we're transforming things into"},{"time":97000,"text":"something that you have absolutely"},{"time":99000,"text":"no reference for."},{"time":101000,"text":"HC: And here's something we have no"},{"time":103000,"text":"reference to eat. This is a cigar, and"},{"time":105000,"text":"basically it's a Cuban cigar made out of"},{"time":107000,"text":"a Cuban pork sandwich, so we take these"},{"time":109000,"text":"spices that go into the pork shoulder,"},{"time":111000,"text":"we fashion that into ash. We take"},{"time":113000,"text":"the sandwich and wrap it up in"},{"time":115000,"text":"a collard green, put an edible label"},{"time":117000,"text":"that bears no similarity to"},{"time":119000,"text":"a Cohiba cigar label, and we put it"},{"time":121000,"text":"in a dollar ninety-nine ashtray and charge"},{"time":123000,"text":"you about twenty bucks for it. (Laughter)"},{"time":126000,"text":"HC: Delicious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128000,"text":"BR: That's not it, though."},{"time":130000,"text":"Instead of making foods that"},{"time":132000,"text":"look like things that you wouldn't eat,"},{"time":134000,"text":"we decided to make ingredients"},{"time":136000,"text":"look like dishes that you know."},{"time":138000,"text":"So this is a plate of nachos."},{"time":140000,"text":"The difference between our nachos"},{"time":142000,"text":"and the other guy's nachos,"},{"time":144000,"text":"is that this is actually a dessert."},{"time":146000,"text":"So the chips are candied,"},{"time":148000,"text":"the ground beef is made from chocolate,"},{"time":150000,"text":"and the cheese is made from a shredded"},{"time":152000,"text":"mango sorbet that gets shredded"},{"time":154000,"text":"into liquid nitrogen to look like cheese."},{"time":156000,"text":"And after doing all of this"},{"time":158000,"text":"dematerialization and reconfiguring"},{"time":161000,"text":"of this, of these ingredients, we realized"},{"time":164000,"text":"that it was pretty cool,"},{"time":166000,"text":"because as we served it, we learned that"},{"time":168000,"text":"the dish actually behaves like the real thing,"},{"time":170000,"text":"where the cheese begins to melt."},{"time":172000,"text":"So when you're looking at this thing"},{"time":174000,"text":"in the dining room, you have this sensation"},{"time":176000,"text":"that this is actually a plate of nachos,"},{"time":178000,"text":"and it's not really until you begin tasting it"},{"time":180000,"text":"that you realize this is a dessert, and"},{"time":182000,"text":"it's just kind of like a mind-ripper."},{"time":185000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":187000,"text":"HC: So we had been creating"},{"time":189000,"text":"all of these dishes out of a"},{"time":191000,"text":"kitchen that was more like"},{"time":193000,"text":"a mechanic's shop than a kitchen, and"},{"time":195000,"text":"the next logical step for us was to install"},{"time":197000,"text":"a state-of-the-art laboratory,"},{"time":199000,"text":"and that's what we have here."},{"time":201000,"text":"So we put this in the basement, and we"},{"time":203000,"text":"got really serious about food, like"},{"time":205000,"text":"serious experimentation."},{"time":207000,"text":"BR: One of the really cool things about"},{"time":209000,"text":"the lab, besides that we have a new"},{"time":211000,"text":"science lab in the kitchen, is that,"},{"time":213000,"text":"you know, with this new equipment, and"},{"time":215000,"text":"this new approach, all these"},{"time":217000,"text":"different doors to creativity that we never"},{"time":219000,"text":"knew were there began to open, and so the"},{"time":221000,"text":"experiments and the food and the dishes"},{"time":223000,"text":"that we created, they just kept going"},{"time":226000,"text":"further and further out there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"HC: Let's talk about flavor transformation,"},{"time":230000,"text":"and let's actually make some cool stuff."},{"time":232000,"text":"You see a cow with its tongue hanging out."},{"time":234000,"text":"What I see is a cow about to eat something"},{"time":236000,"text":"delicious. What is that cow eating?"},{"time":239000,"text":"And why is it delicious?"},{"time":241000,"text":"So the cow, basically, eats three basic"},{"time":243000,"text":"things in their feed: corn, beets, and barley,"},{"time":247000,"text":"and so what I do is I actually"},{"time":249000,"text":"challenge my staff with these crazy,"},{"time":251000,"text":"wild ideas. Can we take what the cow"},{"time":254000,"text":"eats, remove the cow, and then make"},{"time":256000,"text":"some hamburgers out of that?"},{"time":258000,"text":"And basically the reaction tends to be"},{"time":260000,"text":"kind of like this. (Laughter)"},{"time":262000,"text":"BR: Yeah, that's our chef de cuisine,"},{"time":264000,"text":"Chris Jones. This is not the only guy"},{"time":266000,"text":"that just flips out when we assign"},{"time":268000,"text":"a ridiculous task, but a lot of these ideas,"},{"time":271000,"text":"they're hard to understand."},{"time":273000,"text":"They're hard to just get automatically."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275000,"text":"There's a lot of research and a lot of"},{"time":278000,"text":"failure, trial and error -- I guess, more error --"},{"time":281000,"text":"that goes into each and every dish,"},{"time":283000,"text":"so we don't always get it right, and it takes"},{"time":285000,"text":"a while for us to be able to explain that"},{"time":287000,"text":"to people."},{"time":289000,"text":"HC: So, after about a day of Chris and I"},{"time":291000,"text":"staring at each other, we came up with"},{"time":293000,"text":"something that was pretty close"},{"time":295000,"text":"to the hamburger patty, and as you can"},{"time":297000,"text":"see it basically forms like hamburger meat."},{"time":299000,"text":"This is made from three ingredients:"},{"time":302000,"text":"beets, barley, corn, and so it"},{"time":304000,"text":"actually cooks up like hamburger meat,"},{"time":306000,"text":"looks and tastes like hamburger meat,"},{"time":308000,"text":"and not only that, but it's basically"},{"time":311000,"text":"removing the cow from the equation."},{"time":313000,"text":"So replicating food, taking it into that"},{"time":316000,"text":"next level is where we're going."},{"time":318000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":321000,"text":"BR: And it's definitely the world's first"},{"time":323000,"text":"bleeding veggie burger,"},{"time":325000,"text":"which is a cool side effect."},{"time":328000,"text":"And a miracle berry, if you're not familiar"},{"time":330000,"text":"with it, is a natural ingredient, and it"},{"time":332000,"text":"contains a special property."},{"time":334000,"text":"It's a glycoprotein called miraculin,"},{"time":336000,"text":"a naturally occurring thing. It still freaks"},{"time":338000,"text":"me out every time I eat it, but it has a"},{"time":340000,"text":"unique ability to mask certain taste"},{"time":342000,"text":"receptors on your tongue, so that primarily"},{"time":344000,"text":"sour taste receptors, so normally things"},{"time":346000,"text":"that would taste very sour or tart,"},{"time":348000,"text":"somehow begin to taste very sweet."},{"time":351000,"text":"HC: You're about to eat a lemon,"},{"time":353000,"text":"and now it tastes like lemonade."},{"time":355000,"text":"Let's just stop and think about the"},{"time":357000,"text":"economic benefits of something like that."},{"time":359000,"text":"We could eliminate sugar across the board"},{"time":361000,"text":"for all confectionary products and sodas,"},{"time":363000,"text":"and we can replace it with"},{"time":365000,"text":"all-natural fresh fruit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367000,"text":"BR: So you see us here cutting up"},{"time":369000,"text":"some watermelon. The idea with this"},{"time":371000,"text":"is that we're going to eliminate tons of"},{"time":373000,"text":"food miles, wasted energy,"},{"time":376000,"text":"and overfishing of tuna by creating tuna,"},{"time":379000,"text":"or any exotic produce or item"},{"time":382000,"text":"from a very far-away place,"},{"time":385000,"text":"with local, organic produce;"},{"time":388000,"text":"so we have a watermelon from Wisconsin."},{"time":390000,"text":"HC: So if miracle berries take sour things"},{"time":392000,"text":"and turn them into sweet things,"},{"time":394000,"text":"we have this other pixie dust"},{"time":396000,"text":"that we put on the watermelon, and it"},{"time":398000,"text":"makes it go from sweet to savory."},{"time":401000,"text":"So after we do that, we put it into"},{"time":403000,"text":"a vacuum bag, add a little bit of seaweed,"},{"time":405000,"text":"some spices, and we roll it, and this"},{"time":408000,"text":"starts taking on the appearance of tuna."},{"time":410000,"text":"So the key now is to make it"},{"time":412000,"text":"behave like tuna."},{"time":414000,"text":"BR: And then after a quick dip into some"},{"time":416000,"text":"liquid nitrogen to get that perfect sear,"},{"time":419000,"text":"we really have something that looks,"},{"time":421000,"text":"tastes and behaves like the real thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424000,"text":"HC: So the key thing to remember here is,"},{"time":427000,"text":"we don't really care"},{"time":430000,"text":"what this tuna really is."},{"time":432000,"text":"As long as it's good for you and good for"},{"time":434000,"text":"the environment, it doesn't matter."},{"time":436000,"text":"But where is this going?"},{"time":438000,"text":"How can we take this idea of tricking your"},{"time":440000,"text":"tastebuds and leapfrog it into something"},{"time":442000,"text":"that we can do today that could be"},{"time":444000,"text":"a disruptive food technology?"},{"time":446000,"text":"So here's the next challenge."},{"time":448000,"text":"I told the staff, let's just take a bunch"},{"time":450000,"text":"of wild plants, think of them as"},{"time":452000,"text":"food ingredients. As long as they're"},{"time":454000,"text":"non-poisonous to the human body,"},{"time":456000,"text":"go out around Chicago sidewalks,"},{"time":458000,"text":"take it, blend it, cook it and then"},{"time":460000,"text":"have everybody flavor-trip on it at Moto."},{"time":463000,"text":"Let's charge them a boatload of cash for this"},{"time":465000,"text":"and see what they think. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":469000,"text":"BR: Yeah, so you can imagine, a task"},{"time":471000,"text":"like this -- this is another one of those"},{"time":473000,"text":"assignments that the kitchen staff"},{"time":475000,"text":"hated us for. But we really had to almost"},{"time":477000,"text":"relearn how to cook in general,"},{"time":480000,"text":"because these are ingredients, you know,"},{"time":482000,"text":"plant life that we're, one, unfamiliar with,"},{"time":484000,"text":"and two, we have no reference for how"},{"time":486000,"text":"to cook these things because"},{"time":488000,"text":"people don't eat them."},{"time":490000,"text":"So we really had to think about new, creative ways"},{"time":492000,"text":"to flavor, new ways to cook"},{"time":494000,"text":"and to change texture -- and that was"},{"time":496000,"text":"the main issue with this challenge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498000,"text":"HC: So this is where we step into the future"},{"time":501000,"text":"and we leapfrog ahead."},{"time":503000,"text":"So developing nations"},{"time":505000,"text":"and first-world nations,"},{"time":507000,"text":"imagine if you could take these wild plants"},{"time":509000,"text":"and consume them, food miles would"},{"time":511000,"text":"basically turn into food feet."},{"time":513000,"text":"This disruptive mentality of what food is"},{"time":515000,"text":"would essentially open up the encyclopedia"},{"time":518000,"text":"of what raw ingredients are, even if we just"},{"time":520000,"text":"swapped out, say, one of these for flour,"},{"time":522000,"text":"that would eliminate so much energy"},{"time":525000,"text":"and so much waste."},{"time":527000,"text":"And to give you a simple example here as to"},{"time":529000,"text":"what we actually fed these customers,"},{"time":531000,"text":"there's a bale of hay there"},{"time":533000,"text":"and some crab apples."},{"time":535000,"text":"And basically we took hay and crab apples"},{"time":537000,"text":"and made barbecue sauce out of those two ingredients."},{"time":539000,"text":"People swore they were eating"},{"time":541000,"text":"barbecue sauce, and this is free food."},{"time":544000,"text":"BR: Thanks, guys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}